   CASINO-RESTAURANTS (Undated) _ Jean-Georges Vongerichten and
Charlie Palmer are part of the second wave of celebrity chefs
opening casino restaurants in Las Vegas. By Florence Fabricant.
</P>
<P>
   BERRIES (New York) _ Berry prime time: for a couple of weeks,
everything from strawberries to gooseberries are in the markets. By
Florence Fabricant.
</P>
