Internet versions and ``webzines,'' which are found only on the
World Wide Web, and there are more food publications out there than
you can possibly ever read. So, with a warning to be selective,
here are some Internet addresses that, with a press of a button,
will give you instant access to hundreds and hundreds of food and
gourmet magazines. (Pahram, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED
7/28.
