<HEADLINE>
THE GERITOLIZATION OF AMERICAN WORKERS  
 
</HEADLINE>
   (This EXCELLENT ``separate buy'' article is from the current (week
beginning 25 July 1998) Economist magazine.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
