<SLUG> BC-SPORTS-BJT30-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COX NEWS SERVICE THURSDAY SPORTS BUDGET
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   These sports stories for release Thursday, July 30, 1998, are
