<P>
   PBP-DOLPHINS-ARMSTRONG (18 inches) _ DAVIE, Fla. _ Column on
Miami Dolphins defensive end Trace Armstrong. (Skolnick, Palm Beach
Post) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
