   ELEPHANT-PAPA _ (KANSAS CITY, Mo.) _ The Kansas City, Mo., and
Indianapolis zoos are making history by making a baby elephant _
via long distance. The zoos announced Tuesday they have succeeded
in impregnating a female African elephant in Indianapolis with
semen collected from a male in Kansas City. By MATT CAMPBELL. Story
will move in ``a'' category.
</P>
<P>
   POWERBALL-TESTING _ (WEST DES MOINES, Iowa) _ The Powerball
balls are prone to turning yellow over time. But they're kept
beautifully unpredictable. ``We test them four times before each
drawing,'' said Sue Dooley, drawing manager for the Multi-State
Lottery Association that runs Powerball. ``Believe me, we check
everything.'' BY SCOTT CANON. Story will move in ``a'' category.
