allow Maine and Vermont to dump their low-level nuclear waste from
places like the now-closed Maine Yankee in a poor Hispanic town in
west Texas. In a 305-117 vote, the House approved the compact
without any of the troublesome amendments that had been previously
attached to the tri-state deal, setting up a final showdown in the
Senate that will determine its fate. Kane
