<P>
   FBN-SEAHAWKS (Cheney, Wash.) Cortez Kennedy was once the scourge
of training camp, pulling pranks whenever possible and tormenting
teammates. But this summer has seen a gentler, kinder Cortez.
``I've been downright boring,'' he says.
