really deserves a fabulously rich secret father and a wonderfully
wealthy secret mother, plus a fun secret twin sister who will be
her best friend forever? Not many girls turned down ``The Parent
Trap'' fantasy the first time around in 1961, and today's girls
will fall for ``The Parent Trap'' remake all over again. 3 stars.
By BOB FENSTER. Story moved in the ``E`` category. &QL;
