   _ An e-mail now whizzing, unwanted, into mailboxes around the
country is a spam asking users to vote on whether they want to be
spammed. ``Is this adding insult to injury, or what?'' asks  &UR; Flash &LR; 
 &UR; Gordon &LR; . The message gives a 95-cent 900 number.
</P>
