</P>
<P>
   Then again, maybe the unlucky ones aren't those with the wrong
Powerball numbers, but those who hit the lottery a long time ago,
and still don't know it. &QL; 
 &QL; 
E.J. Montini can be reached at ed.montini(at)pni.com via e-mail. &QL;
